<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/7ea00c46aa6b565d6054e18deab891fa2.png"></span><span>Sylvan Strength III</span></dt><dd><div>Increases Sarisse's strength by 2% <br>and critical rate by 1% for 15 seconds<br>for every 20-hit combo.<br><br>Also, using Cheerful Assist will grant Sarisse<br>a strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three and a defense amp with a maximum<br>team amp level of three. After these amps are<br>granted, this ability will not grant them again for<br>20 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8c5aab1cf5fe41020ad4d994b735ba012.png"></span><span>Woodland Blessing III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun and sleep by 100%.<br>When Sarisse is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned or put her to sleep, her strength is<br>increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/58d61047bf07e78f3cf5edd26b2402392.png"></span><span>The Crimson Star</span></dt><dd><div>Increases duration of buff skills by 30%.<br><br>Also, increases attack rate by 10% when the user<br>has a team strength amp and attack skill damage<br>by 20% when the user has a team defense amp.<br>Both of these effects can be applied<br>simultaneously, but neither of them will stack.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1643522400,update_time1643186145